{"tid":1934804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港大醫學院：進入疫情最高風險時候 或出現本地持續爆發","createTime":"2020-03-20T07:19:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T09:50:32.000Z","uid":125168,"like":162,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"56a865326fec838308ad831185199f30efc7c1d7","tid":1934804,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T07:19:04.000Z","msg":"港大醫學院：本港進入自有疫情起最高風險時候<br />\n10分鐘前 Share to Facebook<br />\n【Now新聞台】港大醫學院研究顯示，本港進入自疫情開始以來最高風險的時候，有機會出現本地持續爆發。<br />\n<br />\n研究顯示，本港自上周中期新型冠狀病毒的即時繁殖率，反覆上升至1以上，即患者能將病毒傳播多於一人，反映疫情會繼續擴大。<br />\n<br />\n有份研究的港大公共衞生醫學講座教授梁卓偉指，三月前本港從未出現過持續本地爆發，但近期輸入個案增加，憂慮會發生大型本地爆發，建議商店可縮短營業時間，並加強長者及外傭的防護工作。<br />\n<br />\n他形容市民在二月「眾志成城」防疫，但近期有所鬆懈。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=385042\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D385042&d=wsLpXOxElywvcqXyO2fdBGWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=0446a04c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D385042&h=a774b241\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=385042</a>"},{"pid":"54e5e2f5cbbde9d184c015edd876998d80eeecbe","tid":1934804,"uid":125168,"like":87,"dislike":2,"score":85,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T07:19:18.000Z","msg":"他形容市民在二月「眾志成城」防疫，但近期有所鬆懈。"},{"pid":"ccb8b711e367c48bdaa96df848aa7cbed34c593b","tid":1934804,"uid":125168,"like":66,"dislike":4,"score":62,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T07:19:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">hill office未呀屌你老母</span></span>"},{"pid":"35429c0b942a371aa184cd987afc457a6165c1b6","tid":1934804,"uid":228143,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T07:20:59.000Z","msg":"一星期後鞭佢"},{"pid":"26add46fe38bc24f697ec313755a9d9ef1393195","tid":1934804,"uid":226955,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T07:21:25.000Z","msg":"多謝旅行撚、行